data.description: Discover your dream home in the coveted Dominion Meadows community and zoned for Grassfield HS! This stunning 5 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom house spans 3,015 square feet, a good fit for both family life and entertainment. The first floor has beautiful flooring throughout, leading you to a chef's kitchen, complete with a double oven, ample cabinet and counter space and stylish backsplash. Enjoy gatherings in the screened-in porch or cozy up with a book and coffee on the front porch.  Upstairs, retreat to spacious bedrooms, including a luxurious primary suite with a walk-in closet. A versatile media room on the second floor, for hosting game nights or cozy sleepovers. Plantation shutters on the windows, offer both privacy and charm. The community hosts neighborhood events like a turkey trot, Santa visit, food trucks, chili cook-off and more. Don’t miss a chance to live in a home designed for comfort and community spirit.  Come take a look and experience the magic of Dominion Meadows living!
